These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-1::.
There 5 different types of food: cauliflower, garlic, lettuce, pumpkin, radish
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: pop, punk, salsa, soul, trance
1. the fan of soul is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of soul is in the middle##1
3. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
4. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is between the fan of soul and the fan of salsa##2
6. the person eating radish is in the middle##1
7. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of trance##1
8. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3    |    4    |    5    |
| Food          | garlic | cauliflower | radish | pumpkin | lettuce |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | trance      | soul   | pop     | punk    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, iced-tea, tea, water
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, snowboarding, surfing, swimming, tennis
1. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person drinking water is in the middle##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
5. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's sport is swimming##2
6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |    5    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea     | tea       | water    | almond-milk | fanta   |
| Sport      | snowboarding | badminton | swimming | tennis      | surfing |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, filmmaking, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, electronic, metal, reggae, trance
1. the fan of reggae is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the fan of electronic is in an even position##4
3. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of metal##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
5. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
6. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
8. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3      |     4      |      5      |
| Hobby         | card-games | magic-tricks | filmmaking | reading    | video-games |
| Music-Genre   | reggae     | blues        | metal      | electronic | trance      |

