.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-4::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: chess, puzzles, rock-climbing, sudoku, woodworking
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, martial-arts, satire, scientific, spy
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in the middle##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person watching satire movies and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
7. the person watching spy movies is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |      5       |
| Hobby         | chess      | sudoku | rock-climbing | puzzles   | woodworking  |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | spy    | satire        | adventure | martial-arts |

