.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, mirinda, soy-milk, tea
There are 5 different nationalities: australian, brazilian, canadian, egyptian, japanese
1. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the australian##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the japanese##1
4. the canadian is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
5. the japanese is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the egyptian##1
7. the brazilian is in an even position##4
8. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |     4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | tea      | lemonade | iced-tea   | soy-milk  | mirinda  |
| Nationality   | canadian | egyptian | australian | brazilian | japanese |

