.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-6::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, lemonade, mirinda, tea
The people have 5 different jobs:  electrician, engineer, paramedic, security-guard, software-developer
1. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
2. the engineer is between the software-developer and the person drinking lemonade##2
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the engineer##1
5. the paramedic is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the paramedic is in an even position##4
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
8. the security-guard is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |         2          |    3     |     4     |       5        |
| Beverage   | cola        | 7up                | mirinda  | lemonade  | tea            |
| Job        | electrician | software-developer | engineer | paramedic | security-guard |

