.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-7::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, milk, sprite, water
The people have 5 different jobs:  doctor, electrician, firefighter, librarian, paramedic
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the electrician##3
2. the paramedic is on the left or right of the electrician##3
3. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the firefighter is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
7. the doctor is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
8. the paramedic is on the right of the electrician##1
9. the librarian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |      3      |     4     |       5       |
| Beverage   | water       | milk   | lemonade    | sprite    | hot-chocolate |
| Job        | firefighter | doctor | electrician | paramedic | librarian     |

