.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-9::.
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, egyptian, indian, indonesian, thai
5 different pets are kept: fish, goat, guinea-pig, horse, pony
1. the owner of the fish is in an even position##4
2. the indonesian is the owner of the horse##1
3. the owner of the horse is the indonesian##1
4. the indonesian is on the far right##1
5. the egyptian is the owner of the fish##1
6. the indian is between the egyptian and the chinese##2
7. the owner of the pony is on the right of the indian##1
8. the owner of the goat is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Nationality   | thai | egyptian | indian     | chinese | indonesian |
| Pet           | goat | fish     | guinea-pig | pony    | horse      |

