.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-10::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  accountant, analyst, dancer, firefighter, lawyer
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: rowing, sailing, soccer, swimming, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the lawyer##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's sport is sailing is the accountant##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the accountant##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4
6. the lawyer is on the left of the dancer##1
7. the firefighter is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2    |      3      |     4      |    5    |
| Job     | lawyer | dancer | firefighter | accountant | analyst |
| Sport   | soccer | tennis | swimming    | sailing    | rowing  |

