.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-11::.
There 5 different types of food: broccoli, garlic, pepper, radish, spinach
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, handball, ice-hockey, skateboarding, tennis
1. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
3. the person eating broccoli is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is handball##2
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is tennis is the person eating pepper##1
6. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
7. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |     4      |   5    |
| Food    | garlic    | spinach  | broccoli      | radish     | pepper |
| Sport   | badminton | handball | skateboarding | ice-hockey | tennis |

