.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-12::.
There 5 different types of food: lime, orange, pineapple, plum, pumpkin
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, bus, car, skateboard, trike
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the trike is the person eating lime##1
3. the person driving the trike is in the middle##1
4. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
5. the person driving the bus is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the trike and the person eating orange##2
7. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4
8. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |   3   |     4     |     5      |
| Food        | plum | pumpkin | lime  | pineapple | orange     |
| Transport   | bus  | car     | trike | boat      | skateboard |

