4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is in an even position##4
6. the person drinking iced-tea is between the australian and the person drinking mirinda##2
7. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the mexican##3
8. the australian is on the left of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5     |
