.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-14::.
There 5 different types of food: artichoke, cabbage, grapefruit, pepper, raspberry
The people have 5 different hobbies: board-games, chess, dancing, traveling, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
5. the person eating cabbage is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person eating cabbage##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5      |
| Food    | raspberry   | pepper  | cabbage     | artichoke | grapefruit |
| Hobby   | board-games | dancing | woodworking | traveling | chess      |

