.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-15::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: action, comedy, epic, martial-arts, mystery
There are 5 different nationalities: american, british, chinese, colombian, turkish
1. the american is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
2. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the colombian##3
3. the american is on the left of the chinese##1
4. the chinese is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
5. the british is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
6. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
7. the chinese is in an odd position##4
8. the colombian is in the middle##1
9. the british is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3       |    4     |    5    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | epic    | martial-arts | action   | mystery |
| Nationality   | turkish | british | colombian    | american | chinese |

