4. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
6. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
8. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
9. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |   4    |     5      |
