.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: disco, indie, punk, rock, soul
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, quad-bike, snowmobile, taxi, train
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the fan of soul##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the fan of soul##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the train and the person driving the taxi##2
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the fan of soul##1
5. the fan of rock is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the train is the fan of disco##1
7. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |  3   |    4     |     5      |
| Music-Genre   | disco | punk      | rock | soul     | indie      |
| Transport     | train | quad-bike | taxi | airplane | snowmobile |

